content: About OSU Applied Bioinformatics This website is a joint initiative by bioinformaticians at two Ohio State University centers: the Molecular and Cellular Imaging Center (MCIC; see also our Read-The-Docs site), and the Center for Applied Plant Sciences (CAPS). Here, we collect educational material that aims to empower folks at OSU in using computational tools for their research.
